document_data.name: House Hun'ett
document_data.mainbody: '''House Hun'ett''' was an extinct [[drow]] noble house of [[Menzoberranzan]]. It was formerly the fifth house.<ref><ref>
document_data.Members:
* [[SiNafay Hun'ett]]: Matron Mother, adopted as Shi'Nayne Do'Urden of [[House Do'Urden]] after Hun'ett's fall.<ref>
* [[Masoj Hun'ett]]: Apprentice to Gelroos, killed by [[Drizzt Do'Urden]]<ref>
* [[Gelroos Hun'ett]]: "The Faceless One", slain by Masoj.
* [[Alton DeVir]]: Took the identity of Gelroos and adopted into House Hun'ett after [[House DeVir]] fell.
